25
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:33,740
=A Female Student
Arrives at the Imperial College=

26
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:37,740
=Episod 22=

27
00:01:38,183 --> 00:01:40,823
Bilik dokumentasi ruang untuk membaca.

28
00:01:41,024 --> 00:01:42,784
Pakaian awak memang tidak sesuai.

29
00:01:44,903 --> 00:01:45,984
Apa yang tidak sesuai?

30
00:01:46,263 --> 00:01:46,984
Awak

31
00:01:47,144 --> 00:01:48,984
cuma cemburu melihat orang yang
lebih menarik hati daripada awak.

32
00:01:49,744 --> 00:01:50,464
Cik Song.

33
00:01:50,664 --> 00:01:51,664
Awak baliklah dulu.

34
00:01:51,984 --> 00:01:52,943
Jangan menyusahkan Sang Qi.

35
00:01:53,303 --> 00:01:54,903
Kamu semua hanya menyebelahi Qi.

36
00:01:54,903 --> 00:01:56,024
Saya dah lama rasa tak suka.

37
00:01:56,704 --> 00:01:57,543
Saya takkan pergi dari sini hari ini.

38
00:01:57,744 --> 00:01:58,583
Jika berkebolehan,

39
00:01:59,223 --> 00:02:00,344
awak boleh
bertindak kasar untuk menghalau saya!

40
00:02:01,583 --> 00:02:03,984
Pertama kali saya
dengar permintaan begini.

41
00:02:04,943 --> 00:02:06,104
Kalau begitu,
saya akan berbuat demikian.

42
00:02:06,984 --> 00:02:07,424
Saya...

43
00:02:08,784 --> 00:02:10,424
Awak betul-betul ingin bertindak kasar?

44
00:02:11,104 --> 00:02:12,823
Awak ingat Keluarga Song
hanya hebat atas nama?

45
00:02:13,583 --> 00:02:14,583
Jika mampu,

46
00:02:14,583 --> 00:02:15,984
heretlah sampai saya pergi dari sini!

47
00:02:17,383 --> 00:02:18,344
Kalau begitu, maaf.

48
00:02:22,183 --> 00:02:24,183
Zhuo Wenyuan!

49
00:02:25,103 --> 00:02:25,903
Biar saya turun!

50
00:02:27,543 --> 00:02:28,944
Biar saya turun!

51
00:02:31,704 --> 00:02:32,543
Zhuo Wenyuan!

52
00:02:33,663 --> 00:02:35,344
Biar saya turun!

53
00:02:35,984 --> 00:02:36,784
Qiongyu.

54
00:02:37,103 --> 00:02:37,984
Mari baca buku.

55
00:02:38,344 --> 00:02:39,344
Bersurailah.

56
00:02:39,903 --> 00:02:41,663
Lepaskan tangan! Dengar tak?

57
00:02:41,663 --> 00:02:42,823
Zhuo Wenyuan!

58
00:02:56,383 --> 00:02:58,144
Cik Song, sila lepaskan tangan.

59
00:03:01,543 --> 00:03:02,663
Yin, awak tak apa-apa?

60
00:03:03,623 --> 00:03:04,344
Tuan Muda Zhuo.

61
00:03:04,704 --> 00:03:07,103
Biasanya awak layan perempuan
dengan prihatin,

62
00:03:07,584 --> 00:03:08,623
tak sangka ada juga
sikap yang begitu kasar.

63
00:03:10,304 --> 00:03:11,543
Ya, saya layan perempuan
dengan prihatin,

64
00:03:11,944 --> 00:03:13,584
tapi tak termasuk mereka yang
suka melawan Sang Qi.

65
00:03:14,183 --> 00:03:15,144
Ini ialah bilik dokumentasi,

66
00:03:15,543 --> 00:03:17,424
kamu tak patuhi adat
dan asyik buat bising.

67
00:03:18,263 --> 00:03:19,903
Saya takkan layan orang seperti kamu
dengan baik.

68
00:03:21,784 --> 00:03:23,944
Saya tak pandai lawan cakap,
awak menang.

69
00:03:24,623 --> 00:03:25,903
Namun, Yin berbeza.

70
00:03:26,103 --> 00:03:27,224
Di Bianjing,

71
00:03:27,344 --> 00:03:28,784
Yin tak takut pada sesiapa.

72
00:03:31,183 --> 00:03:31,704
Yin.

73
00:03:34,663 --> 00:03:36,183
Kamu semua menyebelahi Qi

74
00:03:36,183 --> 00:03:37,183
dan suka menindas saya.

75
00:03:37,504 --> 00:03:39,183
Saya yang menang pertaruhan,

76
00:03:39,663 --> 00:03:42,383
tapi, Naib Pengetua Yan bantu dia
mendapat pujian.

77
00:03:42,383 --> 00:03:44,704
Sang Qi dan saya
sama-sama ialah anak orang kaya,

78
00:03:45,183 --> 00:03:46,383
apa perbezaan antara kami?

79
00:03:48,463 --> 00:03:49,224
Saya tahu,

80
00:03:49,944 --> 00:03:52,504
di belakang saya,
kamu kata saya sombong, tak munasabah

81
00:03:52,543 --> 00:03:53,704
dan tak tahu kemampuan diri,

82
00:03:53,704 --> 00:03:54,784
tapi, itu cuma kerana

83
00:03:54,784 --> 00:03:56,903
saya jatuh hati pada seseorang.

84
00:03:57,224 --> 00:03:58,304
Apa salah saya?

85
00:03:58,784 --> 00:04:00,743
Apa salah saya? Apa salah saya?

86
00:04:01,103 --> 00:04:01,623
Baiklah.

87
00:04:02,263 --> 00:04:02,543
Saya...

88
00:04:02,784 --> 00:04:03,543
Awak bawa bertenang.

89
00:04:04,224 --> 00:04:05,183
Jika awak teruskan mengecoh,

90
00:04:05,704 --> 00:04:06,224
awak lagi malu.

91
00:04:12,463 --> 00:04:13,424
Apa awak buat?

92
00:04:13,903 --> 00:04:14,864
Tak buat apa-apa.

93
00:04:15,263 --> 00:04:18,704
Awak tak selalu nampak jahil dan comel.

94
00:04:18,704 --> 00:04:20,263
Saya tak benarkan awak cakap begitu.

95
00:04:21,984 --> 00:04:22,543
Saya...

96
00:04:22,944 --> 00:04:24,343
Saya bukan mencaci awak.

97
00:04:24,864 --> 00:04:25,744
Saya rasa,

98
00:04:27,864 --> 00:04:28,503
rupa awak ini

99
00:04:28,943 --> 00:04:30,823
lebih comel daripada sikap awak
yang sombong.

100
00:04:31,543 --> 00:04:33,543
Apa kata awak tukar gaya awak?

101
00:04:33,584 --> 00:04:35,464
Comel?

102
00:04:37,343 --> 00:04:37,783
Baiklah.

103
00:04:38,663 --> 00:04:39,783
Jangan marah pada Sang Qi lagi.

104
00:04:41,184 --> 00:04:43,063
Saya kalah kepada Yan Yunzhi
dalam pertarungan demi perkahwinan.

105
00:04:43,464 --> 00:04:44,383
Saya lebih malu

106
00:04:44,943 --> 00:04:46,063
berbanding dengan awak.

107
00:04:50,783 --> 00:04:51,744
Kenapa lagi?

108
00:04:55,263 --> 00:04:56,304
Kamu akan balik rumah nanti, kan?

109
00:04:57,464 --> 00:04:58,904
Tunggu saya sekejap, saya hantar kamu.

110
00:05:07,263 --> 00:05:07,783
Yin.

111
00:05:10,624 --> 00:05:11,984
Mengapa awak tercegat?

112
00:05:13,624 --> 00:05:14,864
Tak apa-apa.

113
00:05:28,503 --> 00:05:29,904
Cik Song, mari kita pergi.

114
00:05:42,584 --> 00:05:43,223
Ayah.

115
00:05:47,584 --> 00:05:51,503
Bukankah awak Tuan Muda Zhuo yang
sangat terkenal kebelakangan ini?

116
00:05:52,503 --> 00:05:55,103
Mengapa awak boleh datang ke sini?

117
00:05:55,103 --> 00:05:57,624
Ayah, Tuan Muda Zhuo
menghantar saya pulang ke sini.

118
00:05:58,984 --> 00:06:02,144
Kalau begitu, terima kasih.

119
00:06:03,584 --> 00:06:04,383
Tuan Muda Zhuo.

120
00:06:04,704 --> 00:06:06,223
Saya dah sampai ke rumah.

121
00:06:06,543 --> 00:06:07,503
Awak pulanglah dulu,

122
00:06:07,783 --> 00:06:08,864
kita ajak berjumpa lagi lain kali.

123
00:06:14,263 --> 00:06:15,024
Jiayin.

124
00:06:15,704 --> 00:06:17,424
Awak pergi rehat di dalam bilik dulu.

125
00:06:24,464 --> 00:06:25,063
Tutor Besar Song.

126
00:06:25,624 --> 00:06:26,744
Saya nak berbincang dengan awak.

127
00:06:29,943 --> 00:06:30,984
Jemput ke bilik bacaan saya.

128
00:06:33,744 --> 00:06:34,343
Silakan.

129
00:06:39,383 --> 00:06:41,584
Apa dia? Cakaplah.

130
00:06:42,383 --> 00:06:43,464
Tutor Besar Song, awak ingat tak,

131
00:06:43,624 --> 00:06:44,984
bilik sisi yang disita sebelum ini?

132
00:06:47,624 --> 00:06:48,503
Saya masih ingat.

133
00:06:50,063 --> 00:06:51,383
Bukankah ia dah selesai?

134
00:06:52,584 --> 00:06:53,943
Tutor Besar Song,
awak mungkin dah lalai.

135
00:06:54,783 --> 00:06:56,024
Saya nak tanya,

136
00:06:57,103 --> 00:06:58,464
adakah awak pernah gunakan
bilik sisi itu untuk

137
00:06:58,864 --> 00:07:00,304
beli raksi kepada Cik Song?

138
00:07:10,663 --> 00:07:12,144
Betul.

139
00:07:14,424 --> 00:07:15,584
Kalau begitu, awak mesti berhati-hati.

140
00:07:16,783 --> 00:07:17,823
Awak

141
00:07:18,663 --> 00:07:19,584
mungkin akan diawasi.

142
00:07:33,184 --> 00:07:34,464
Ini benarkah?

143
00:07:35,184 --> 00:07:36,144
Kemungkinan besarnya benar.

144
00:07:36,864 --> 00:07:38,663
Awak mesti buat perancangan
terlebih dahulu.

145
00:08:17,543 --> 00:08:18,864
Saya bukan mencaci awak.

146
00:08:20,184 --> 00:08:21,144
Saya rasa,

147
00:08:21,823 --> 00:08:22,543
rupa awak ini

148
00:08:23,304 --> 00:08:25,024
lebih comel daripada sikap awak
yang sombong.

149
00:08:25,823 --> 00:08:27,823
Apa kata awak tukar gaya awak?

150
00:08:37,503 --> 00:08:38,263
Ke tepi!

151
00:08:38,263 --> 00:08:39,064
Pergi!

152
00:08:39,064 --> 00:08:39,384
Saya...

153
00:08:41,103 --> 00:08:43,143
Tak pernah sesiapa berani
tolak perempuan di depan saya.

154
00:08:56,184 --> 00:08:58,064
Wahai Song Jiayin!

155
00:08:58,064 --> 00:08:59,103
Kenapa dengan awak?

156
00:08:59,624 --> 00:09:00,543
Awak mesti ingat,

157
00:09:01,184 --> 00:09:03,223
awak akan jadi isteri Naib Pengetua Yan,

158
00:09:03,583 --> 00:09:04,744
tak boleh fikir lelaki lain.

159
00:09:09,624 --> 00:09:11,023
Namun,

160
00:09:12,463 --> 00:09:15,583
Tuan Muda Zhuo satu daripada
Empat Tuan Muda Bianjing

161
00:09:16,223 --> 00:09:17,384
dan mendapat tempat pertama
dalam peperiksaan diraja.

162
00:09:18,143 --> 00:09:19,703
Tadi, ayah juga cakap

163
00:09:19,824 --> 00:09:21,184
dia amat terkenal
dalam kerajaan sekarang,

164
00:09:22,103 --> 00:09:23,744
boleh dikatakan setanding
dengan Naib Pengetua Yan.

165
00:09:24,744 --> 00:09:27,864
Yang paling penting,
dia layan saya dengan berbeza.

166
00:09:31,663 --> 00:09:32,663
Saya mahu

167
00:09:32,663 --> 00:09:34,703
berkahwin dengan lelaki yang
paling cemerlang di Bianjing,

168
00:09:35,944 --> 00:09:39,264
tapi, dua lelaki ini masing-masing
ada kelebihan sendiri.

169
00:09:40,223 --> 00:09:43,184
Kalau perlu pilih satu daripada mereka,

170
00:09:43,184 --> 00:09:45,663
saya rasa serba salah.

171
00:09:49,984 --> 00:09:53,783
Antara ikan dengan telapak beruang,

172
00:09:57,624 --> 00:09:59,463
yang mana satu patut saya pilih?

173
00:10:05,690 --> 00:10:08,740
(Hanya menerima pelajar cemerlang)

174
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:10,740
(Pertemuan Golongan
Pujangga Kuno dan Moden)

175
00:10:12,504 --> 00:10:13,783
Dulu, tak tahu pun ada banyak buku

176
00:10:13,783 --> 00:10:14,984
yang disimpan di Maktab Diraja.

177
00:10:15,424 --> 00:10:17,583
Alangkah bagusnya jika boleh
diterima untuk belajar di sini.

178
00:10:18,064 --> 00:10:19,304
Apa yang awak fikir itu?

179
00:10:19,343 --> 00:10:21,504
Dulu, Maktab Diraja hanya terima
anak dari keluarga ternama.

180
00:10:21,504 --> 00:10:23,304
Kini, ia terima pendaftaran
secara terbuka.

181
00:10:23,343 --> 00:10:24,783
Kalau awak diterima,

182
00:10:24,783 --> 00:10:26,463
awak patut bersyukur.

183
00:10:28,984 --> 00:10:29,944
Biar saya tolong.

184
00:10:37,463 --> 00:10:38,583
Semua di sini baik-baik sahaja,

185
00:10:39,184 --> 00:10:41,023
tapi terdapat seorang cikgu perempuan,

186
00:10:41,304 --> 00:10:42,944
langsung tak masuk akal.

187
00:10:43,184 --> 00:10:44,504
Saya dengar bahawa

188
00:10:44,543 --> 00:10:46,424
Pendokumen Sang boleh masuk
belajar di Maktab Diraja

189
00:10:46,424 --> 00:10:49,264
kerana ayahnya ialah Komandan Agung.

190
00:10:50,424 --> 00:10:53,103
Membuka pendaftaran kepada
semua keluarga ini mungkin bermaksud

191
00:10:53,783 --> 00:10:55,944
membuka pendaftaran kepada
keluarga berada seperti

192
00:10:55,944 --> 00:10:58,143
Keluarga Sang.

193
00:10:58,504 --> 00:10:59,663
Betul.

194
00:11:11,023 --> 00:11:12,143
Betul cakap awak.

195
00:11:12,783 --> 00:11:14,783
Saya mendapat perlindungan
daripada keluarga

196
00:11:14,783 --> 00:11:16,624
untuk belajar di Maktab Diraja,

197
00:11:17,184 --> 00:11:18,504
tapi, saya mendapat

198
00:11:18,504 --> 00:11:19,504
jawatan pendokumen

199
00:11:19,984 --> 00:11:21,424
dengan bergantung pada usaha sendiri.

200
00:11:21,984 --> 00:11:23,824
Awak pandai cakap saja.

201
00:11:23,824 --> 00:11:24,463
Betul.

202
00:11:24,463 --> 00:11:25,624
Saya boleh buktikan.

203
00:11:25,903 --> 00:11:26,343
Baik,

204
00:11:27,184 --> 00:11:29,223
tapi, jangan buktikan dengan
kemahiran menunggang dan memanah.

205
00:11:29,663 --> 00:11:31,384
Awak belajarnya di rumah awak,

206
00:11:31,744 --> 00:11:33,023
tak ada kaitan dengan Maktab Diraja.

207
00:11:33,223 --> 00:11:34,103
Tentulah.

208
00:11:34,783 --> 00:11:36,783
Jika saya tulis kajian ilmiah di sini,

209
00:11:36,783 --> 00:11:38,824
mungkin akan bazirkan masa kamu.

210
00:11:38,824 --> 00:11:40,543
Bilik dokumentasi adalah tempat
di mana saya bertugas.

211
00:11:40,903 --> 00:11:43,343
Apa kata kita

212
00:11:43,343 --> 00:11:44,304
jalani ujian di sini?

213
00:11:45,223 --> 00:11:46,343
Macam mana nak menguji?

214
00:11:46,343 --> 00:11:47,903
Terdapat lebih 100 jenis buku di sini,

215
00:11:47,903 --> 00:11:49,424
jumlahnya ribuan buku.

216
00:11:49,463 --> 00:11:50,543
Bilangannya banyak,

217
00:11:50,543 --> 00:11:52,103
tapi saya ingat benar setiap buku.

218
00:11:52,103 --> 00:11:53,504
Mana-mana sebuah buku yang awak sebut,

219
00:11:53,543 --> 00:11:54,384
asalkan ia ada di sini,

220
00:11:54,384 --> 00:11:55,543
saya boleh cari untuk awak.

221
00:11:56,064 --> 00:11:56,624
Baik.

222
00:11:57,304 --> 00:11:58,184
"Penghuraian Hujah Laozi".

223
00:11:58,583 --> 00:11:59,624
Ini tak sukar untuk awak, kan?

224
00:12:00,023 --> 00:12:01,903
"Penghuraian Hujah Laozi".

225
00:12:10,023 --> 00:12:11,384
"Penghuraian Hujah Laozi",

226
00:12:12,304 --> 00:12:15,384
dikarang oleh Yan Zun,
pertapa Tao Dinasti Han Barat,

227
00:12:19,663 --> 00:12:20,864
menyampaikan pendapat dia terhadap
hujah Laozi

228
00:12:21,264 --> 00:12:23,160
dengan rangkap.

229
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,543
Namun, saya mencadangkan supaya

230
00:12:25,064 --> 00:12:26,984
membaca buku ini bersama

231
00:12:27,184 --> 00:12:28,384
"Heshang Gong",

232
00:12:28,384 --> 00:12:29,864
mungkin akan menemui
pengetahuan yang di luar jangkaan.

233
00:12:34,384 --> 00:12:35,103
Macam mana?

